ện, đắc hôn tự - 閬州東樓筵奉送十一舅往青城縣，得昏字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Qu%C3%A1-C%E1%BB%95-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-eU5Yiq91O05-fUiKqmLXNw">Quá Cổ Châu - 過古州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%C3%BD-ca-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BA%B7ng-C%C3%B4ng-An-Nhan-th%E1%BA%ADp-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-th%E1%BB%89nh-C%E1%BB%91-b%C3%A1t-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-b%C3%ADch/poem-OmQxrd4OxiuGOfZIDuWp0A">Tuý ca hành tặng Công An Nhan thập thiếu phủ thỉnh Cố bát đề bích - 醉歌行贈公安顏十少府請顧八題壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/V%E1%BB%8B-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-1/poem-yIiB1CvO03hSPWN3YdWiVA">Vị Dương 1 - 渭陽 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-2-T%C3%A1p-t%C3%A1p-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-phong-t%E1%BA%BF-v%C5%A9-lai/poem-X4IVK-A_G4R2U3Jm30HjHw">Vô đề tứ thủ kỳ 2 (Táp táp đông phong tế vũ lai) - 無題四首其二（颯颯東風細雨來）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
